milestones.description: Noor Ali and Shahzad's 39-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 28 between Mohammad Nabi and Noor Ali
Samiullah Shinwari and Asghar Afghan's 48-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 16 between Samiullah Shinwari and Hasti Gul
Samiullah Shinwari and Mirwais's 17-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 3 between Khaliq Dad and Hasti Gul
Samiullah Shinwari has become the top scorer for AFG in ODIs with 79 runs, going past Mohammad Nabi's 58
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Noor Ali's 2
Samiullah Shinwari has conceded the most runs in an innings (56) in ODIs for AFG, going past Hasti Gul's record of 48
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Noor Ali's 2
Asghar Afghan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for AFG, going past Dawlat

stories.title: ten Doeschate class sinks Afghanistan
stories.subTitle: Netherlands v Afghanistan, 1st ODI, Amstelveen
stories.summary: Ryan ten Doeschate used all his all-round experience to deny Afghanistan their second ODI victory, in a tense encounter at Amstelveen which Netherlands won by eight runs
